### 普通用户模块接口测试 (User Module)

@base_url = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

# 🚨 将下方的 Token 替换为您从 auth.http 登录后获得的真实 access_token
@auth_token = Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI3M2RhNTRkYy03Nzc1LTQ2NjktYjhjNS0yZTlhNjU4MWJhMjQiLCJyb2xlIjoiVXNlciIsImlzcyI6ImNyb3dkZnVuZGluZ19wcmFjdGljZSIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzkzNDExMSwiZXhwIjoxNzczOTM1MDExfQ.OUyyunMo18Vj0zj2WB8Dj20gFgDZFDdPm-_cBsDbUVk

### 1. 获取自己的完整信息
GET {{base_url}}/users/me
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### 2. 更新个人可见资料 (支持局部更新)
PUT {{base_url}}/users
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "NewTestUser",
    "age": 26
    // "gender" 是可选的
}

### 3. 修改密码
PATCH {{base_url}}/users/password
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "old_password": "password123",
    "new_password": "newpassword456"
}

### 4. 彻底退网 (软删除自己)
# 警告：执行此操作后，当前 Token 及账号将被注销！
DELETE {{base_url}}/users/me
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
